FlightGear.ArdControl - Control FlightGear aircrafts with external Tx/Rx system for RC airplanes.

Add protocol files to Flightgear from Protocols/*
Run Flightgear using run.bat
Upload Rxreader/Rxreader.pde to Arduino board.
Connect Tx/Rx system.
Run C# program and connect to Ardunio and Flightgear.

That's all :).

